thread.title_full: BRIEF-Stanusch Technologies gets order for virtual advisor technology | Reuters

author: Reuters
title: BRIEF-Stanusch Technologies gets order for virtual advisor technology
text:
Sept 21 Stanusch Technologies SA :
* Gets an order from teamLeaders Sp. z o.o. Sp. K. to deliver the company virtual advisor technology to JZO Sp. Z o.o.
* The value of the deal has not been disclosed Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage: (Gdynia Newsroom)
